import React from 'react';
import { Box, Typography, Paper, Container } from '@mui/material';

function ApiDocumentation() {
    return (
        <Container maxWidth="md" sx={{ mt: 4 }}>
            <Paper elevation={3} sx={{ p: 4 }}>
                <Typography variant="h4" component="h1" gutterBottom>
                    API Documentation
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
                    This page contains documentation for the ChatSecure API.
                </Typography>
                
                <Box sx={{ mt: 4 }}>
                    <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                        Authentication
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
                        All API endpoints require authentication using JWT tokens provided by Keycloak.
                        Include the token in the Authorization header as a Bearer token.
                    </Typography>
                </Box>
                
                <Box sx={{ mt: 4 }}>
                    <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                        Endpoints
                    </Typography>
                    
                    <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
                        GET /api/chats
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
                        Returns a list of all chats for the authenticated user.
                    </Typography>
                    
                    <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
                        POST /api/chats
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
                        Creates a new chat. Requires a JSON body with chat details.
                    </Typography>
                    
                    <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
                        GET /api/messages/{'{chatId}'}
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
                        Returns messages for a specific chat.
                    </Typography>
                    
                    <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
                        POST /api/messages
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
                        Sends a new message. Requires a JSON body with message content and chat ID.
                    </Typography>
                </Box>
            </Paper>
        </Container>
    );
}

export default ApiDocumentation;
